Package: pottsMixture
Type: Package
Title: Fits latent Potts models
Version: 1.0
Date: 2017-04-06
Author: Stephen Berg [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Stephen Berg <saberg2@wisc.edu>
Description: Fits latent Potts models. The model fits and simulation results in the paper "A Latent Discrete Markov Field Approach For Identifying and Classifying Historical Forest Communities Based on Spatial Multivariate Tree Species Counts" were generated using this package.
License: MIT
Imports: Rcpp (>= 0.12.8), RcppEigen (>= 0.3.2.9.0), data.table (>= 1.10.0.0)
Depends: igraph, permute, Matrix
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppEigen
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
